title: Election Simulation
new-page: true
set-jump: post_election_sim

The Election Simulation system is an in-game tool used for debugging and testing. Do play around with historic election results and see how the game handles them!

- @2012_11: Catalan Parlament (November 2012)
- @2015_9: Catalan Parlament (September 2015)
- @2015_12: Spanish Congreso (December 2015)
- @about: Back
# - @2017_12: Catalan Parlament (December 2017)

