**Block results**
{!<table style='border-spacing: 0px; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; width:95%; table-layout: fixed;'>!}
{!<tr><td style='width: !}[+ independence_parlament_pv +]{!%'>Independence</td>!}{!<td style='text-align: center; width: !}[+ nonaligned_parlament_pv +]{!%'>Unaligned</td><td style='text-align: right; width: !}[+ unionist_parlament_pv +]{!%'>Union</td></tr>!}
{!<tr><td style='height: 2em; background-color: #008000; color: white; text-align: center; border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;'>!}**[+ independence_parlament_pv +]%**{!</td><td style='background-color: #b1b0aeff; color: black; text-align: center'>!}**[+ nonaligned_parlament_pv +]%**{!</td><td style='background-color: #fe0101; color: white; text-align: center; border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0;'>!}**[+ unionist_parlament_pv +]%**{!</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}
{!<div style="font-style: italic; margin-top: -1em; margin-left: 3em">Popular vote</div>!}

{!<table style='border-spacing: 0px; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; width:95%; table-layout: fixed; margin-top:-0.75em;'>!}
{!<tr><td style='overflow:hidden; white-space: nowrap; width: !}[+ independence_parlament_spc +]{!%; height: 2em; background-color: #008000; color: white; text-align: center; border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;'>!}**[+ independence_parlament_s+]** ([+ independence_parlament_spc +]%) {!</td><td style='overflow:hidden; white-space: nowrap; width: !}[+ nonaligned_parlament_spc +]{!%; background-color: #b1b0aeff; color: black; text-align: center'>!}**[+ nonaligned_parlament_s+]** ([+ nonaligned_parlament_spc +]%) {!</td><td style='overflow:hidden; white-space: nowrap; width: !}[+ unionist_parlament_spc +]{!%; background-color: #fe0101; color: white; text-align: center; border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0;'>!}**[+ unionist_parlament_s+]** ([+ unionist_parlament_spc +]%) {!</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}
{!<div style="font-style: italic; margin-top: -1em; margin-left: 3em">Parlament control</div>!}

[? if ciu_parlament_s > 0 : Note: <span style='color: #002782; font-weight: bold;width:95%;'>CiU</span> has been unclear about their position on independence, so it is counted as unaligned. ?]
[? if jxsi_parlament_s > 0 : Author's note: I am aware that in this simulation the pro-independence parties get a majority of the votes instead of a plurality. I do not know if I'll fix it, because I only used the weights as a rough guide, not as something set in stone. ?]

**Government Formation**
# yeah this is hardcoded because its only the simulation scenes

[? if ciu_parlament_showviz: <span style='color: #002782; font-weight: bold;'>CiU</span> will be able to form a <span style='color: #002782; font-style: italic;'>minority government</span> with <span style='color: #ff8000; font-weight: bold;'>ERC</span>'s external support. ?]

[? if jxsi_parlament_showviz: <span style='color: #3ab6a5; font-weight: bold;'>JxSí</span> will need <span style='color: #ffed00; font-weight: bold;'>CUP</span>'s external support to form a <span style='color: #3ab6a5; font-style: italic;'>Sovereignty government</span>. ?]

